n=top align=left class=m><span class=title> SoL &quot;Sanctuary&quot; Spell question</span><hr size=1> I recently received the level 9 spell &quot;Sanctuary,&quot; one of the new SoL spells.   When it is cast it says that &quot;target (whomever) is at peace.&quot;  When I cast it on myself and I walk by a mob, it says &quot;a sarnak Legionnaire has triggered your sentinel.&quot;  What exactly does this spell do?  Does it keep mobs from attacking you?  Wondering... <br>
